I also disapprove quad-kiting for the game's sake, although I do it (I'm so eager to reach level 52 to get Tears of Druzzil...)<P>But, if they want to nerf quad-kiting, they can do it in a very easy and non-disruptive way (of which they are aware) which is: shorten drastically the RANGE of the Columns/Pillars (so, you will still be able to use the spells in group play, but not in kiting, as the mobs will come and hit you before the spell is completed, in spite of the Snare).<P>Visit my AE spall guide: <A HREF="http://perso.wanadoo.fr/nicolbolas/wizae.html" TARGET=_blank>http://perso.wanadoo.fr/nicolbolas/wizae.html</A><P>--------------------<P>Nicolbolas says: "Prepare to meet the skilled fury of an Erudin whizz".
